00:54:24.899 --> 00:54:26.780
I know when we first talked to Rachel about this,

00:54:26.780 --> 00:54:28.979
we were like, maybe 10 to 12 people wanna chat

00:54:28.979 --> 00:54:33.219
about this problem that we have constantly in this space.

00:54:33.219 --> 00:54:35.340
