I know I shared a bunch of the questions

00:55:09.699 --> 00:55:10.580
with you ahead of time.

00:55:10.580 --> 00:55:12.899
Was there anything you thought was gonna come up today

00:55:12.899 --> 00:55:15.860
that we didn't get a chance to talk about?

